00:00:49.350 --> 00:00:52.340
We get that right from
this slope intercept

00:00:52.340 --> 00:00:55.774
form of the equation, slope
is equal to negative 4.

00:00:55.774 --> 00:00:57.190
And they ask us,
what is the limit

00:00:57.190 --> 00:00:59.710
as x approaches negative 1
of all of this kind of stuff?

00:00:59.710 --> 00:01:02.110
So let's plot the
point negative 1.

