So when x is
negative 1, so that's

00:01:03.980 --> 00:01:05.610
this point right over here.

00:01:05.610 --> 00:01:10.630
And this point right over here
would be the point negative 1,

00:01:10.630 --> 00:01:12.660
g of negative 1.

