So what they're
doing right over here

00:01:25.030 --> 00:01:29.310
is they're finding the slope
between an arbitrary point x, g

00:01:29.310 --> 00:01:31.530
of x, and this point
right over here.

00:01:31.530 --> 00:01:32.410
So let's do that.

00:01:32.410 --> 00:01:34.330
So let's take another x.

00:01:34.330 --> 00:01:35.510
So let's say this is x.

