for the slope between
negative 1 and g of negative 1

00:02:52.710 --> 00:02:54.840
and an arbitrary x.

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:59.040
Well, we already know that
no matter what x you pick,

00:02:59.040 --> 00:03:03.180
the slope between x, g of , and
