00:03:06.090 --> 00:03:08.310
It's going to be
equal to negative 4.

00:03:08.310 --> 00:03:11.620
This thing is going to
be equal to negative 4.

00:03:11.620 --> 00:03:13.640
It's going to be
equal to negative 4.

00:03:13.640 --> 00:03:16.760
Doesn't matter how close
